  "texts": [
    "A diverse array of machine learning and deep learning methodologies are employed in this investigation.",
    "Saeed et al. [20] discussed a technique to enhance accuracy in facial recognition.",
    "Their proposed CNN method (fall detection-CNN), incorporating two hidden layers and four convolutional layers, serves as an automated framework.",
    "Utilizing the expanded Cohn-Kanade (CK+) dataset, which includes images portraying a range of emotions from various individuals, the process encompasses pre-processing, feature extraction, and categorization.",
    "The model's effectiveness is evaluated through metrics such as F1-score, recall, and precision, with respective values of 84.07%, 78.22%, and 94.09%."
